<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="explanation-n">explanation <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ˌeksplə'neɪʃn/    美 /ˌeksplə'neɪʃn/  </p>
<p>[C] &amp; [U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>解释；说明：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>make an explanation
作说明/进行解释</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They hope that they can find an <strong>explanation for</strong> the attacks.
他们希望能找出这些袭击事件的原因。</p><footer>北师大④ – 11</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He left the room <strong>without explanation</strong>.
他未加解释就离开了房间。</p></div></div>